<h3 class="text-lg text-accent font-bold">CAPA:</h3>
<p>Corrective and preventive action (CAPA or simply corrective action) consists of improvements to an organization's processes taken to eliminate causes of non-conformities or other undesirable situations. It is usually a set of actions, laws or regulations required by an organization to take in manufacturing, documentation, procedures, or systems to rectify and eliminate recurring non-conformance. Read more about CAPAs <a class="link link-accent" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corrective_and_preventive_action">here</a>.</p>
